CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FPolling conducted for ITV News by
OL,7,FIpsos of more than a thousand UK
OL,8,Fadults found that those who oppose the
OL,9,Fassisted dying bill fear the risk of
OL,10,Fabuse or misuse of the law if it were
OL,11,Fto be passed.
OL,13,FUK Editor Paul Brand has met with
OL,14,FNicola Waters, who was diagnosed with
OL,15,Fmotor neurone disease six years ago.
OL,16,FNicola's fear is that disabled people
OL,17,Fmay be coerced into an assisted death,
OL,18,Feither by external influences or by
OL,19,Ftheir own internalised vulnerabilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
