FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FNicola Waters has one big ambition: to
OL,7,Flive to see her youngest son turn 18.
OL,9,FHer two boys were only seven and four
OL,10,Fwhen she was diagnosed with motor
OL,11,Fneurone disease (MND) six years ago.
OL,13,FSince then, she has significantly
OL,14,Foutlived the average prognosis for the
OL,15,Fdisease of two to three years.
OL,17,FBut in that time, the 51-year-old says
OL,18,Fshe has lost much of her independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,F"Now my youngest son can't remember me
OL,7,Fwalking", she tells ITV News' UK
OL,8,FEditor Paul Brand. "I haven't been
OL,9,Fable to hug my children for a few
OL,10,Fyears, but they hug me, thankfully."
OL,12,F"I need help with everything. I can't
OL,13,Freally do anything myself,
OL,14,Funfortunately. To wash, to get
OL,15,Fdressed, to go to the loo, to make
OL,16,Ffood, to make cups of tea."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@HO]pD@TOUrD@dO]tD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FWe're meeting Nicola as the House of
OL,7,FLords considers passing an assisted
OL,8,Fdying bill, which would allow
OL,9,Fterminally ill people with less than
OL,10,Fsix months left to live to be helped
OL,11,Fto die.
OL,13,FNicola's MND is a grey area in the
OL,14,Flaw, and it is unclear whether
OL,15,Fpatients with the disease would
OL,16,Fqualify.
OL,18,FBut Nicola would not want the option
OL,19,Fregardless, because she feels that the
OL,20,Fbill is a danger to disabled people
OL,21,Flike her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,F"I think a lot of people speak to me
OL,7,Fas if I'm a child", she says,
OL,8,Fexplaining her experience of the way
OL,9,Fsociety perceives disabled people.
OL,11,F"Sometimes people talk over me as if
OL,12,FI'm not really there, and it's very
OL,13,Ffrustrating.
OL,15,F"When you have a terminal illness like
OL,16,FMND, people imagine that your life is
OL,17,Fnot really worth living and that if
OL,18,Fthey were in your situation, perhaps
OL,19,Fthey wouldn't want to live."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@RO]sD@AOUwD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FNicola's fear is that disabled people
OL,7,Fmay be coerced into an assisted death,
OL,8,Feither by external influences or by
OL,9,Ftheir own internalised vulnerabilities.
OL,11,FIt is a fear shared by others in an
OL,12,Fexclusive poll for ITV News carried
OL,13,Fout by Ipsos.*
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FWhen those opposing the bill stated
OL,7,Ftheir reasons for doing so, the most
OL,8,Fcommonly provided answers relate to:
OL,9,Fthe need to focus on life, rather than
OL,10,Fdeath (26%), disagreeing with the
OL,11,Fprinciple of assisted dying (26%) and
OL,12,Fthe risk of abuse or misuse of the
OL,13,Flaw, including in relation to
OL,14,Fvulnerable people (23%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FOverall, the poll found that 65% of
OL,7,Fpeople either strongly support or tend
OL,8,Fto support the assisted dying bill,
OL,9,Fcompared to 14% who either strongly
OL,10,Foppose or tend to oppose it, but
OL,11,Fopponents of the bill say polling does
OL,12,Fnot capture the full detail of the
OL,13,Fdebate.
OL,15,FITV News is speaking to people on both
OL,16,Fsides of the argument as the assisted
OL,17,Fdying bill runs out of time in the
OL,18,FHouse of Lords, where peers have
OL,19,Ftabled more than 1,200 amendments to
OL,20,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FAmong them is the former Paralympian,
OL,7,FBaroness Tanni Grey-Thompson.
OL,9,F"I'm not opposed to the principle of
OL,10,Fassisted suicide, but the bill in
OL,11,Ffront of us has so many loopholes, and
OL,12,Fit's just really vaguely written, and
OL,13,FI'm really worried about the potential
OL,14,Ffor coercion for disabled people", she
OL,15,Ftold me, among other concerns.
OL,17,F"It's the risk of people not feeling
OL,18,Fvalued by society and feeling that
OL,19,Fthey have no other choice but to end
OL,20,Ftheir lives."
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@aO]yD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FThe peer says claims that some
OL,7,Fopponents of assisted dying have tried
OL,8,Fto filibuster the bill in the House of
OL,9,FLords by laying so many amendments are
OL,10,Funfair.
OL,12,F"We have been accused of
OL,13,Ffilibustering, but I don't feel that
OL,14,Fpeople are acting in bad faith. Our
OL,15,Frole is to amend, to make things
OL,16,Fbetter. We need to look at this issue
OL,17,Fin a different way - at the whole of
OL,18,Fpeople's care and support, not just
OL,19,Fmaking it easy for them to end their
OL,20,Flives."
OL,26,@tD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,FThat view is shared by Nicola, who has
OL,7,Fwatched every hour of the debate in
OL,8,Fthe House of Lords and wants peers to
OL,9,Fensure that the bill does not pass.
OL,11,FShe is currently supported by carers
OL,12,Fwho visit her three times a day, and
OL,13,Fshe worries about those who cannot
OL,14,Faccess that level of assistance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,F"It makes a huge difference for me.
OL,7,FI'm not sure I could live, certainly
OL,8,Fnot with dignity and comfort, without
OL,9,Fthe support I get from my amazing
OL,10,Fcarers. And it does worry me where
OL,11,Fpeople cannot access that care, how
OL,12,Fthat then makes them feel about
OL,13,Fcarrying on living."
OL,15,FNicola feels confident that the care
OL,16,Fshe receives will allow her to live in
OL,17,Fcomfort until the very end of her life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774173985
OL,3,CTerminally ill mother says peers must
OL,4,Creject assisted dying
OL,6,F"I think with the care that I am lucky
OL,7,Fenough to have and the doctors that I
OL,8,Fhave looking after me, I know that
OL,9,Fthey will keep me still living without
OL,10,Fbeing in distress", she says.
OL,12,F"I have to make the best of every day
OL,13,Fthat I can."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
